TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Differential Approach to Dominant Strategy Mechanisms
AU  - Laffont, Jean-Jacques
AU  - Maskin, Eric
AB  - [This paper shows how a number of questions about dominant strategy mechanisms in models with public goods can be conveniently formulated as systems of partial differential equations. The question of the existence of dominant strategy mechanisms with given desirable properties becomes equivalent to the integrability of these equations.]
